### Assembly Line Setup at position(14.5, 14.5)

- Multiple burner inserters at positions (14.5, 12.5), (12.5, 14.5), (16.5, 14.5)
- Multiple wooden chests at positions (14.5, 11.5), (11.5, 14.5), (17.5, 14.5)

### Electronic Circuit Production at position(21.5, 15.5)
Consists of:

- Burner inserters at positions (19.5, 15.5), (23.5, 15.5)
- Wooden chest at (24.5, 15.5)

### Power Generation Setup
Consists of:
- Three offshore pumps at positions (-7.5, 25.5), (2.5, 34.5), and (2.5, 36.5)
- Boiler at (18.0, 47.5)
- Steam engine at (29.5, 51.5)
- Extensive pipe network connecting these components

ERROR TIPS

### Errors when attempting to extract items from empty containers
- Ensure the source container has the required items before attempting extraction
- Wait for production to complete before attempting to collect items

### Power system connectivity issues
- Ensure all electrical components are properly connected to power network
- Check that steam engines have proper fluid connections and water supply

### Production line stalling issues
- Ensure proper fuel supply to burner inserters and furnaces
- Check that assembling machines have all required input materials
- Verify proper connection of inserters between storage and production facilities

### Fluid system connectivity problems
- Ensure proper pipe connections between offshore pumps, boilers and steam engines
- Check that pipes form complete paths for fluid transfer
